@@ Deploy sequence for my sample voting application:

- deploy mongo_configmap.yaml
- deploy mongo_secret.yaml
- deploy mongo_pod.yaml
- deploy mongo_service.yaml
- deploy voting_app_pod.yaml
- deploy voting_app_service.yaml
- deploy voting_result_app_pod.yaml
- deploy voting_result_app_service.yaml

Deploying gateway and virtualservice (continuation):

- deploy voting_app_gateway.yaml	(istio (ingress) gateway)
- deploy voting_virtual_service.yaml  	
  (exposes host and forwards request to gateway which inturn forwards to "voting-app-service")